{"tid":1029850,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"第一次見，一邊 interview, 一邊食煙","createTime":"2019-02-20T14:06:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-20T16:30:21.000Z","uid":79786,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1b2ab8d73d3a0817f0e3b23dede1a51ea9964be5","tid":1029850,"uid":79786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T14:06:38.000Z","msg":"最近，見咗間通訊設備公司，真係大開眼界。<br />\n<br />\n1st In, 就 In HR 個阿Head, 對方係好nice, 不過呢，我坐係房到，等咗成55分鐘先有得In.<br />\n<br />\n好啦，叫做過咗HR嗰關，話即係見老細做2nd In.<br />\n<br />\n點知呢，一坐低，對方就自動點煙了。仲要呢，佢一路食煙，一路向住我塊面噴煙。我真係覺得好唔尊重，心惗，搞錯呀。<br />\n<br />\n而且，我明明見另一個職位，嗰個腦細竟然話，不如考慮下做Sales 先，做得好Sales, 就先轉份去原本見嗰個職位。<br />\n<br />\n最後，我只有禮貌地話，唔好意思，我惗Sales未必適合我呀，多謝你哋今日嘅時間。<br />\n<br />\n走人時，真係覺得，呢個interview真係第一次遇見呢D遭遇，真係浪費咗半日嘅時間。"},{"pid":"d15de508de6a1e7c934fd88dbf912c9078e6bc80","tid":1029850,"uid":43983,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T14:11:01.000Z","msg":"開名啦 夠膽開post屌唔夠膽開名比大家睇路"},{"pid":"63d6d9d98f4ce3dfa0ac50850546cc96258fdb6b","tid":1029850,"uid":169487,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d15de508de6a1e7c934fd88dbf912c9078e6bc80","tid":1029850,"uid":43983,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T14:11:01.000Z","msg":"開名啦 夠膽開post屌唔夠膽開名比大家睇路"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T14:26:38.000Z","msg":"做sales先賺到錢"},{"pid":"de7535f94f19be872afbd7d21fc57ac628abe7a9","tid":1029850,"uid":30454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T14:28:11.000Z","msg":"開名啦"},{"pid":"4ac15456f5cb11590e25c3b989d0c9c79c8773f2","tid":1029850,"uid":61018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T14:28:59.000Z","msg":"名呢"},{"pid":"a18c1a13d3a28ab58067eae1395a8bd1c426c76b","tid":1029850,"uid":34442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T14:34:14.000Z","msg":"煲煙噴面咁撚痴線?"},{"pid":"0f663da377a3b069767a70d2103f730d3165cb61","tid":1029850,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-